# Adab branding

## Colors (Tailwind tokens)

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `adab-navy-800` | `#1B2A4A` | Primary text, buttons |
| `adab-navy-900` | `#0F1A2E` | Dark backgrounds |
| `adab-gold-500` | `#C9A227` | Accents, CTAs |
| `adab-cream` | `#F8F6F1` | Page background |
| `adab-gray-300/500` | — | Borders, secondary text |

## Typography

- Display: Plus Jakarta Sans (`font-display`)
- Body: Inter (`font-body` / default)

## Logo & assets

- Primary logo: `/brand/logo.png`
- Favicon: `/brand/favicon.ico`
- OG image: `/brand/og-image.png`
- Brand kit ZIP: `/brand/adab-brand-kit.zip`
- Office templates: `/brand/downloads/office/` (business card, letterhead, flyer, email signature)

## UI patterns

- Rounded corners: `rounded-xl` inputs, `rounded-2xl` cards, `rounded-full` buttons
- Shadows: `shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(27,42,74,0.08)]` on cards
- Buttons: navy primary on public site, gold accent for highlights
- Portal/admin: use `portal-*` CSS classes

## Do not

- Use generic blue/purple gradients off-brand
- Replace CAC seal with Adab logo (CAC is registration display only)
- Hardcode phone/email — use `siteConfig` from `@/lib/site-config`
